        </p>

        <h3>Step 4: Wait for Invitation</h3>
        <p>
          BC PNP conducts regular draws for healthcare occupations, typically weekly. If your score meets or exceeds the draw cut-off, you will receive an Invitation to Apply (ITA). Healthcare draws typically have lower cut-offs (60-100) compared to general draws (115+).
        </p>

        <h3>Step 5: Submit Complete Application</h3>
        <p>
          After receiving an invitation, you have <strong>30 calendar days</strong> to submit your full application with supporting documents, including:
